The library consists of two parts:
	* pseudo-terminal handling (as in "vt100-like", not in "pty")
	  These parts are documented in "man libtty".
	* ttyrec files
	  For documentation, look at "man libttyrec".

The utilities are:
	* termrec
	* termplay
	* termtime
	* termcat

